original_title: X-TrainFit Circuit Burnout 90 - Sport Yoga Upper Body
overview: Similar to the Lower Body Sport Yoga workout, you will go through a series of poses that work the entire body, with an added focus on the upper body.  The light dumbbells are an option that gives you more of a challenge to further rev your metabolism and tone your upper body.
title: X-TrainFit Circuit Burnout 90 - Sport Yoga Upper Body
